Description:
    This is for adding scene to your app/assets/
    for 1st time please execute,
    `bundle exec rails generate pixijs_starter:install`
    for 2nd time and later
    `bundle exec rails generate pixijs_starter:add your_scene_name`

Example:
    rails generate pixijs_starter Thing

    This will create:
        app/assets/javscripts/pixijs/scenes/
